{"data":[{"date":"16:23 20/06","title":"Juventus b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t cho Real v\u00e0 Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/7/13/miralem-pjanic-juventus-2.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 khi m\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pjanic \u201c\u0111\u1eaft kh\u00e1ch\u201d tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus t\u1eeb AS Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 32 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016, Miralem Pjanic l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. Anh l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Bianconeri su\u1ed1t 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Pjanic trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Juventus l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai s\u00e1nh b\u1eb1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Pjanic, l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c Juventus b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. L\u1ea5y v\u00ed d\u1ee5 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua. Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng khai th\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/7/13/miralem-pjanic-juventus-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pjanic, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 anh. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/juventus-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-man-city-voi-gia-50-trieu-bang-172-187858.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus t\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n sao kh\u1ee7ng cho Man City v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span>. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea3 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 cao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Juventus th\u1eeba hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Miralem Pjanic v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. T\u1edd Tuttosport m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a tin Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 70,4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Andres Iniesta chia tay Barca\" title=\"tien ve Andres Iniesta chia tay Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/De-Jong-khong-muon-toi-Barca-trong-tuong-lai-gan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca \u0111ang c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Iniesta</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Barca \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao sau khi Andres Iniesta sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u201cd\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u00e0\u201d. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00fang ra \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n Andre Gomes, Denis Suarez \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf khi \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 Barca h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang trong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Barca ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ea3 t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Pjanic. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u201cc\u00e2u gi\u1edd\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00fd mu\u1ed1n. H\u1ecd tin n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia ch\u1eadm ch\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng. R\u1ed3i c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Man City hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00e1ch Pjanic s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u0169 50 tri\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-sao-bu-juventus-172-187781.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/Monaco-muon-dua-Gonzalo-Higuain-roi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-sao-bu-juventus-172-187781.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 sao b\u1ef1 Juventus</span><br>\r\n<span>Sau Chelsea, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Monaco c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gonzalo Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-juventus-len-ke-hoach-rut-ruot-mu-172-188254.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/hlv-juventus-len-ke-hoach-rut-ruot-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-juventus-len-ke-hoach-rut-ruot-mu-172-188254.html\">HLV Juventus l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u201cr\u00fat ru\u1ed9t\u201d MU</span><br>\r\n<span>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. HLV Massimiliano Allegri \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"391","checkdouble":"189062"},{"date":"16:26 20/06","title":"HLV Morocco: \"R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Ronaldo l\u00fac n\u00e0y\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/hlv-morocco-rat-kho-de-ngan-chan-ronaldo-luc-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Herve Renard c\u1ee7a Morocco th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p n\u00e0o h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00f4m nay.</h2><h2>Morocco \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u sinh t\u1eed\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morocco kh\u00f3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Ronaldo l\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Morocco kh\u00f3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Ronaldo l\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/hlv-morocco-rat-kho-de-ngan-chan-ronaldo-luc-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Morocco th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc Phi s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Luzhniki h\u00f4m nay. V\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Morocco l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Ph\u00eda b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Ronaldo \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao. Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hat-trick t\u1ea1i World Cup khi n\u00e3 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Morocco kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n Ronaldo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-maroc-19h00-ngay-206-an-tu-dau-tien-421-188986.html\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Morocco</span>, HLV Renard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c ngh\u0129 ra m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ronaldo c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cK\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Ronaldo th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. \u00cdt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o. Ho\u1eb7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ec1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 phi th\u01b0\u1eddng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u1eeb \u2018phi th\u01b0\u1eddng\u2019 c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu c\u1eed 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo k\u00e8m Ronaldo th\u00ec ph\u1ea7n thua c\u0169ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. B\u1edfi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1eddi. V\u1eady n\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Morocco:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-maroc-19h00-ngay-206-an-tu-dau-tien-421-188986.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c (19h00 ng\u00e0y 20/6): \u00c1n t\u1eed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-dt-bo-dao-nha-phu-nhan-su-phu-thuoc-vao-ronaldo-421-188979.html\">HLV \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"390","checkdouble":"189066"},{"date":"16:38 20/06","title":"CLB HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn l\u1ea1i \"ng\u1ef1a quen \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169\"?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/6/clb-hagl-noi-gi-sau-khi-tang-tien-lai-ngua-quen-duong-cu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan t\u01b0\u1edbng Somyot Poompanmoung \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia trong khu v\u1ef1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034.</h2><h2>Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y li\u00ean minh M\u1ef9- Canada- Mexico \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2026. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y nhi\u1ec1u qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034 c\u00f9ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034 c\u00f9ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/viet-nam-thai-lan-len-ke-hoach-dang-cai-world-cup-2034.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng cai VCK World Cup 2034</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1eeba qua, \u00f4ng Tengku Abdullah Sultan Ahmad Shah, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u1ee6y ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh FIFA v\u00e0 l\u00e0 C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Malaysia cho r\u1eb1ng Th\u00e1i Lan - Vi\u1ec7t Nam - Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u00ean li\u00ean quan c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 World Cup. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 Ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan (FAT), Somyot Poompanmoung \u0111\u00e3 thay m\u1eb7t ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n r\u1eb1ng, th\u00f4ng tin Th\u00e1i Lan mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c World Cup 2034 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u1eefng s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n, th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 sao hay c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u01a1 s\u1edf h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng giao th\u00f4ng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c World Cup th\u00ec hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Malaysia v\u00e0 Indonesia l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cVi\u1ec7c Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c World Cup hay l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc ASEAN \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Malaysia hay Indonesia l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 quan nh\u1ea5t\u201d, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u FAT nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Trung Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng l\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c gia s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 gi\u00e0u c\u00f3 v\u1ec1 kinh t\u1ebf c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u SV\u0110 l\u1edbn trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, vi\u1ec7c Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t VCK World Cup l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"389","checkdouble":"189067"},{"date":"16:53 20/06","title":"Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p trai ng\u1eddi ng\u1eddi, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Senegal v\u1eabn \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/khong-dep-trai-ngoi-ngoi-thuyen-truong-senegal-van-an-tuong-nhat-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i qua l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, v\u00e0 HLV Aliou Cisse g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n&ldquo;So\u00e1i ca&rdquo; s\u01a1 mi tr\u1eafng Aliou Cisse<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua (19/6), Nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa s\u01b0 t\u1eed Teranga \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ti\u1ebfng vang l\u1edbn, khi b\u1ebb c\u00e1nh \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng Ba Lan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1. Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Senegal tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n 9/10 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u1ec9 ra Sadio Mane. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ng\u00f4i sao Liverpool kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5y thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a anh &ndash; HLV Aliou Cisse c\u1ee7a \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia Senegal. V\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00e1 \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh c\u00f9ng m\u00e1i t\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 phai v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Aliou Cisse l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u0103m 2002, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Senegal l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u tham d\u1ef1 World Cup trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft sau khi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110KV\u0110 Ph\u00e1p. Cisse ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Senegal v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Aliou Cisse g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"HLV Aliou Cisse g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/cise2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Aliou Cisse g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi m\u00e1i t\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u00f4ng t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T U23 Senegal v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012. Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2013-2015, Cisse tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd. T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u00f4ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Senegal \u0111o\u1ea1t v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ebfn Nga v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i (4 th\u1eafng, 2 h\u00f2a sau 6 tr\u1eadn).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV c\u00f3 v\u1ebb ngo\u00e0i tr\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t rapper n\u00e0y c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;th\u1ea7n th\u00e1i&rdquo; c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 42 tu\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V ph\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i World Cup \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 32 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ra s\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0o phong c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 Aliou Cisse.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh HLV Aliou Cisse g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Ba Lan<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Aliou Cisse g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Aliou Cisse t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Senegal t\u1ea1i World Cup 2002\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/cisse.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Aliou Cisse t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Senegal t\u1ea1i World Cup 2002</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Aliou Cisse g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"HLV Aliou Cisse c\u1ee7a \u0110T Senegal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/8/cise.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Aliou Cisse c\u1ee7a \u0110T Senegal t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Aliou Cisse g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Cisse b\u1eaft tay v\u1edbi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1ed