"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/cdv-senegal-duoc-tan-duong-vi-hanh-dong-don-rac-tren-svd-461-189008.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/cdv-senegal-duoc-tan-duong-vi-hanh-dong-don-rac-tren-svd.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/cdv-senegal-duoc-tan-duong-vi-hanh-dong-don-rac-tren-svd-461-189008.html\">C\u0110V Senegal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1n d\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ecdn r\u00e1c tr\u00ean SV\u0110</span><br>\r\nH\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Senegal sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Ba Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ca ng\u1ee3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-ba-lan-12-senegal-bang-h-world-cup-2018-461-188974.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/tong-hop-ba-lan-12-senegal-bang-h-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-ba-lan-12-senegal-bang-h-world-cup-2018-461-188974.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ba Lan 1-2 Senegal (B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp, Morocco, Nigeria v\u00e0 Tunisia bi\u1ebfn Senegal th\u00e0nh ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi trong lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-aliou-cisse-chia-se-sau-tran-thang-cua-dt-senegal-465-188975.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/hlv-aliou-cisse-chia-se-sau-tran-thang-cua-dt-senegal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-aliou-cisse-chia-se-sau-tran-thang-cua-dt-senegal-465-188975.html\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Ba Lan, HLV \u0110T Senegal t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o ch\u00e2u Phi</span><br>\r\nHLV Aliou Cisse chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o Phi ch\u00e2u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Senegal tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"388","checkdouble":"189068"},{"date":"16:53 20/06","title":"S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 15: \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i ph\u00e1o\u201d so t\u00e0i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-15-dai-phao-so-tai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 15 xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Sau cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Clip S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 15:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WQAHpxyelYM\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, James Rodr\u00edguez \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a World Cup 2014. \u1ede v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Colombia \u0111\u00e3 ghi 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Hy L\u1ea1p, B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. T\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Uruguay (c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap) v\u00e0 Brazil (1 b\u00e0n), James c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u201cn\u1ed5 s\u00fang\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n c\u1ea3 th\u1ea3y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i James tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lionel Messi d\u00f9 2 si\u00eau sao \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c nhau. Trong khi Ronaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick \u1edf tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u00f2a T\u00e2y Ban Nha 3-3 th\u00ec Messi kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng \u201ct\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i\u201d m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng penalty trong tr\u1eadn Argentina b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n 1-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch l\u00e0m b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 qua l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng Ronaldo c\u1ea1nh tranh gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 m\u00e0 S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 15 li\u1ec7t k\u00ea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e3y gh\u00e9 th\u0103m Bongda24h.vn th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt nh\u1eefng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup!<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean k\u00eanh Youtube c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-3-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p1-421-188173.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/10/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-3-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-3-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p1-421-188173.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 3: \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (P1)</span><br>\r\n<span>Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u00e2u, Bongda24h.vn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi clip S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 3. H\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng nhau b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111i\u1ec3m...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-5-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p2-421-188290.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-5-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-5-diem-mat-cac-cuu-vuong-the-gioi-p2-421-188290.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 5: \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (P2)</span><br>\r\n<span>S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 \u0111i qua 3 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n t\u1eebng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nong-bongda24hvn-so-huu-ban-quyen-song-cung-world-cup-2018-421-188075.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/8/nong-bongda24hvn-so-huu-ban-quyen-song-cung-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nong-bongda24hvn-so-huu-ban-quyen-song-cung-world-cup-2018-421-188075.html\">N\u00d3NG: Bongda24h.vn s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t serie S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\n<span>Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, VTV \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n World Cup 2018, m\u00f3n \u0103n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00f2m th\u00e8m su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e8 t\u1edbi gi\u1edd. H\u00f2a...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBongda24h.vn (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"387","checkdouble":"189069"},{"date":"16:54 20/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f9ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/nguoi-thai-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-cung-viet-nam-dang-cai-world-cup-2034.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan t\u01b0\u1edbng Somyot Poompanmoung \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia trong khu v\u1ef1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034.</h2><h2>Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y li\u00ean minh M\u1ef9- Canada- Mexico \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2026. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y nhi\u1ec1u qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034 c\u00f9ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034 c\u00f9ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/viet-nam-thai-lan-len-ke-hoach-dang-cai-world-cup-2034.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng cai VCK World Cup 2034</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1eeba qua, \u00f4ng Tengku Abdullah Sultan Ahmad Shah, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u1ee6y ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh FIFA v\u00e0 l\u00e0 C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Malaysia cho r\u1eb1ng Th\u00e1i Lan - Vi\u1ec7t Nam - Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u00ean li\u00ean quan c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 World Cup. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 Ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan (FAT), Somyot Poompanmoung \u0111\u00e3 thay m\u1eb7t ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n r\u1eb1ng, th\u00f4ng tin Th\u00e1i Lan mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c World Cup 2034 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u1eefng s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n, th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 sao hay c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u01a1 s\u1edf h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng giao th\u00f4ng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c World Cup th\u00ec hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Malaysia v\u00e0 Indonesia l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cVi\u1ec7c Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c World Cup hay l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc ASEAN \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Malaysia hay Indonesia l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 quan nh\u1ea5t\u201d, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u FAT nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Trung Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng l\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c gia s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 gi\u00e0u c\u00f3 v\u1ec1 kinh t\u1ebf c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u SV\u0110 l\u1edbn trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, vi\u1ec7c Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t VCK World Cup l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"386","checkdouble":"189070"},{"date":"17:13 20/06","title":"G\u1eb7p \u201ch\u00e0ng l\u1edfm\u201d, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Trung Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/gap-hang-lom-dt-u19-viet-nam-dai-thang-tran-dau-tren-dat-trung-quoc.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u1eb7p h\u00e0ng l\u1edfm, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Trung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u1eb7p h\u00e0ng l\u1edfm, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Trung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Gap-hang-lom,-DT-U19-Viet-Nam-dai-thang-tran-dau-tren-dat-Trung-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1eeb 15 -25/6/2018 t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u, Trung Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 18/6, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a CLB Meizhou Mexian Techand. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n ch\u01a1i l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 l\u1ea7n s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u2018qu\u00e2n xanh\u2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, khi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n h\u1ecd Ho\u00e0ng tung \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 ghi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa \u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 6-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u2018qu\u00e2n xanh\u2019 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng song HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Meizhou Mexian Techand c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i B c\u1ee7a CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 24/6 t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\">VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nL\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i Jarkata, Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, U19 \u00dac. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/dtqg/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten-292-188565.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/dtqg/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten-292-188565.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n, HAGL g\u00f3p 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 25 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 v\u00e0 U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-boc-tham-vck-u19-chau-a-2018-15h00-ngay-185-372-186574.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/17/truc-tiep-boc-tham-vck-u19-chau-a-2018-15h00-ngay-185.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-boc-tham-vck-u19-chau-a-2018-15h00-ngay-185-372-186574.html\">B\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f9ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Australia</span><br>\r\nTheo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c AFC ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh t\u1ea1i Indonesia, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"385","checkdouble":"189071"},{"date":"17:28 20/06","title":"HLV S\u00e0i G\u00f2n b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u00ec b\u1ecb mang ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i cho \u0111i\u1ec3m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/22/hlv-sai-gon-buc-xuc-vi-bi-mang-tieng-duoc-ha-noi-cho-diem.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec b\u1ecb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn cho r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1edf k\u1ecbch.</h2><h2>HLV S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u00ec chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 12 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi 1 b\u00e0n trong khi ngo\u1ea1i binh Da Sylva l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa poker b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-2 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u00ec b\u1ecb mang ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i cho \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u00ec b\u1ecb mang ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i cho \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/22/hoa-ha-noi-fc-hlv-phan-van-tai-em-do-tai-cho-ao-cua-btc.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i\u1ec3m</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1edfi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, HLV T\u00e0i Em t\u1ecf ra h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn. Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch AFF Cup 2008 chia s\u1ebb: \u201cH\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 b\u1edfi khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng th\u00ec quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Ng\u1ecdc Duy gi\u00fap S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng ai \u0111\u00e3 xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cNh\u1eefng ai xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ra sao \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00ec b\u1ecb s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi cu\u1ed9c kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng. Anh em trong \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00f2ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u00ec S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC m\u1edbi nu\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hy v\u1ecdng tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111ang t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam: <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/lich-thi-dau-25.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, BXH V-League 2018</strong></span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung-168-188784.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung-168-188784.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u00e0o sau t\u1ea5m m\u00e0n nhung?</span><br>\r\nTrong c\u01a1n m\u01b0a n\u1eb7ng h\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t chi\u1ec1u qua, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u00fac th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang x\u1ebfp \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho-291-188777.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho-291-188777.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf xin - cho?</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf xin - cho v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i \u1edf V-League, b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nghi v\u1ea5n quanh tr\u1eadn thua...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nam-dinh-co-chien-thang-dau-tay-tren-san-nha-hlv-sai-gon-chi-uoc-1-dieu-168-188430.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/nam-dinh-co-chien-thang-dau-tay-tren-san-nha-hlv-sai-gon-chi-uoc-1-dieu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nam-dinh-co-chien-thang-dau-tay-tren-san-nha-hlv-sai-gon-chi-uoc-1-dieu-168-188430.html\">CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, HLV S\u00e0i G\u00f2n ch\u1ec9 \u01b0\u1edbc 1 \u0111i\u1ec1u</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV S\u00e0i G\u00f2n Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm g\u1eb7p tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"384","checkdouble":"189073"},{"date":"17:38 20/06","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Nga 3-1 Ai C\u1eadp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-nga-31-ai-cap.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nga \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ai C\u1eadp v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Denis Cheryshev</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-0 c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia, Denis Cheryshev ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Thay-gi-sau-tran-Nga-vs-Ai-Cap-bang-A-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Denis Cheryshev ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDenis Cheryshev l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0110T Nga \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp, m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1edbi 4 l\u1ea7n. Ph\u00fat 59, t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a Mario Fernandes, Cheryshev c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 kh\u1edfi tranh Cheryshev c\u00f3 11 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 trong 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCheryshev \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nga c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 3 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Ronaldo c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. N\u1ebfu Cheryshev ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u0103ng hoa anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Nga ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Artem Dzyuba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ai C\u1eadp, HLV Stanislav Cherchesov c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nga \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Artem Dzyuba thay v\u00ec Smolov. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Artem Dzyuba\" title=\"Artem Dzyuba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/dyzuba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Artem Dzyuba c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong su\u1ed1t hi\u1ec7p 1, nh\u1eefng pha treo b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb hai bi\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Dzyuba g\u00e2y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Ai C\u1eadp. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn m\u1edbi gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 62, t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, Artem Dzyuba kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua 2 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp r\u1ed3i tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhanh nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec7n khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n M. El-Shenawy ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ecn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Dzyuba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1eadp nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp b\u1edfi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 ghi 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o ch\u1ec9 sau 20 ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn Nga vs Ai c\u1eadp b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Nga, Dzyuba s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Smolov \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Uruguay&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uruguay c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng vui nh\u1ea5t khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Nga \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ai C\u1eadp 3-1, b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Nga l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Uruguay vui mung khi Nga danh bai Ai Cap\" title=\"Uruguay vui m\u1eebng khi Nga \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ai C\u1eadp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/uruguay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Uruguay vui m\u1eebng khi Nga \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ai C\u1eadp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u00e1t khao ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Saudi Arabia s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Uruguay v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 99%, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 T\u00e2y Ban Nha ho\u1eb7c B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Ahmed Fathy</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Ahmed Fathy \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Cheryshev b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0110T Nga. Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u0103ng ngang v\u00e0o trong.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ahmed Fathy phan luoi nha\" title=\"Ahmed Fathy ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/phan-luoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ahmed Fathy ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7p 2 m\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 ph\u00fat, Ahmed Fathy trong m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1edfi Ai C\u1eadp ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00ecm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1, khi d\u00e2ng cao h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 gi\u00fap Nga c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAhmed Fathy l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 5 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u1edf World Cup 2018 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Mohamed Salah</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay, Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah khong the giup Ai Cap danh bai Nga\" title=\"Salah kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/salah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Salah kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nga</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Salah kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n khi gi\u00fap Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 qu\u1ea3 11m v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi r\u1eddi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1 2018 khi\u1ebfn Liverpool ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid, Salah l\u1ea1i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n n\u1eefa khi c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm \u1edf VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ai C\u1eadp l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf World Cup 2018 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Salah c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111ua tranh danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Hector Cuper</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Hector Cuper \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, \u00f4ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Ai C\u1eadp g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hector Cuper\" title=\"Hector Cuper\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/hlv-hector-cuper-chi-ra-ly-do-khien-ai-cap-that-bai-truoc-nga.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hector Cuper c\u00f9ng Ai C\u1eadp g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAi C\u1eadp ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHector Cuper c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Salah hay trong tay \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, song r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng Ai&nbsp;C\u1eadp th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n*Squawka</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"383","checkdouble":"189075"},{"date":"17:49 20/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1ea1o r\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Ma R\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-ma-roc-va-du-doan-bo-dao-nha-vs-ma-roc.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Ma R\u1ed1c c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa c\u1ee7a CR7 c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-bo-dao-nha-vs-ma-roc-463-189049.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/link-xem-bo-dao-nha-vs-ma-roc.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-bo-dao-nha-vs-ma-roc-463-189049.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c 19h00 ng\u00e0y 20/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Ma r\u1ed1c: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Morocco b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 l\u00fac...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u:</em> B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Ma R\u1ed1c<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian:</em> 19h ng\u00e0y 20/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m:</em> S\u00e2n Luzhniki (th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Moskva)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha -0.92*0:1*0.87 Ma R\u1ed1c<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Nhi\u1ec1u 0.88*2 1/4*-0.95 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Bo Dao Nha vs Maroc\" title=\"Preview B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-ma-roc-va-du-doan-bo-dao-nha-vs-ma-roc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Ma R\u1ed1c 19h ng\u00e0y 20/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi (O 2 1/4)</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. C\u00fa hat-trick bao g\u1ed3m qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o b\u00e3 tr\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33, Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n n\u0103ng n\u1ed5, bao s\u00e2n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh h\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2u m\u00e0 l\u1ea7n. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Ma R\u1ed1c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ngay Ronaldo hoa than thanh\" title=\"Ng\u00e0y Ronaldo h\u00f3a th\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/bai-du-thi-ngay-ronaldo-hoa-than-thanh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo l\u1eadp hat-trick tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha, m\u1ecdi \u00e1nh m\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f5i theo Ronaldo song kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb ch\u00fat t\u00e2m l\u00fd n\u00e0o. Kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 4 n\u0103m n\u1eefa CR7 c\u00f3 c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf World Cup tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Qatar hay kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn 2014 l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng anh c\u00f2n c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u00e1y h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng s\u1ebd m\u1edf toang c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda t\u1edbi Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 6 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p cho ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1985.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-morocco-rat-kho-de-ngan-chan-ronaldo-luc-nay-469-189066.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/hlv-morocco-rat-kho-de-ngan-chan-ronaldo-luc-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-morocco-rat-kho-de-ngan-chan-ronaldo-luc-nay-469-189066.html\">HLV Morocco: R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Ronaldo l\u00fac n\u00e0y</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV Herve Renard c\u1ee7a Morocco th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p n\u00e0o h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00f4m nay.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n13 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Ronaldo ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang derby b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, anh l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh? R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn h\u00f2a oanh li\u1ec7t v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Ma R\u1ed1c thua c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B l\u00e0 Iran c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BDN doi hinh\" title=\"BDN doi hinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/dt-bo-dao-nha-tai-world-cup-2018-khong-con-la-ronaldo-team.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec7 tinh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm. H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Seleccao hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ngo\u00e0i Ronaldo c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c. Nh\u1eefng Goncalo Guedes, Bernardo Silva, Joao Mario, Andre Silva, Gelson Martins r\u1ed3i c\u1ea3 Ricardo Quaresma&hellip; \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng &ldquo;tr\u1ee3 th\u1ee7&rdquo; \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c cho CR7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu c\u00f2n nghi ng\u1edd v\u00e0o h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Pepe hay Jose Fonte, ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra c\u1edfi m\u1edf v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. C\u00f2n Ma R\u1ed1c, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maroc phan luoi\" title=\"Maroc phan luoi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Nhan-dinh-Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Maroc-(19h00-ngay-206)-An-tu-dau-tien-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ma R\u1ed1c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn thua Iran khi\u1ebfn Ma R\u1ed1c t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng B v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o 2 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh gi\u1eadt l\u1ea1i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi h\u01a1n l\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng,<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ecdng l\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 c\u1ee7a Ma R\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran \u0111a ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n 68%, tung ra 13 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng chung cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu c\u1ea3nh tr\u1eafng tay b\u1edfi b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Aziz Bouhaddouz ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Ma R\u1ed1c mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga v\u00e0 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i qu\u00ean \u0111i m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u: T\u1eadp th\u1ec3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u1ebft. V\u00e0 c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 v\u1edbi &ldquo;S\u01b0 t\u1eed v\u00f9ng Atlas&rdquo; l\u00e0 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3n hi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Ma R\u1ed1c bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i. C\u1ea7n t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1eaft chiu h\u01a1n n\u1eefa c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat nh\u01b0 Ayoub El Kaabi, Hakim Ziyech hay Younes Belhanda&hellip; v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n, Ma R\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, t\u1ed1i nay, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 C\u0110V c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</strong><br>\r\n- Ma R\u1ed1c ghi t\u1edbi 30 b\u00e0n sau 11 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup (trong b\u00ecnh g\u1ea7n 3 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn)<br>\r\n- B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 2/7 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua<br>\r\n- Trong 7 tr\u1eadn n\u00f3i tr\u00ean, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 11 l\u1ea7n<br>\r\n- 5/6 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng </strong>(kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia-va-du-doan-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia-421-189017.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia-va-du-doan-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia-va-du-doan-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia-421-189017.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c cho tr\u1eadn Uruguay v