:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 Boateng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br />\r\nXe t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ee9t x\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc El Tri<br />\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 (th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch), nh\u01b0ng \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Joachim Loew \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 ngay tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Mexico, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thua 0-1.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00cdt ng\u00e0y sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m l\u1ea1c quan, nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bayern Munich cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00f3 m\u1eb7c to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Boateng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico \" title=\"Boateng vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/sao-tuyen-duc-thua-nhan-chien-thuat-sai-lam-trong-tran-thua-mexico.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Boateng&nbsp;l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;V\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m \u1edf m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n ba s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a khi \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn, ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u01a1n.&rdquo;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/thuy-dien-vs-han-quoc-bang-f-463-188813.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span>, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf kh\u00f3. Trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo, Boateng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh k\u1ebb ch\u1ea7u r\u00eca ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Manuel Neuer cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang mong ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t SV\u0110 m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 m\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. R\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ngay sau \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng.&rdquo;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Boateng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lozano-ghi-ban-ha-guc-duc-mot-cdv-mexico-bat-ngo-lay-duoc-vo-421-188930.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/lozano-ghi-ban-ha-guc-duc-mot-cdv-mexico-bat-ngo-lay-duoc-vo.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lozano-ghi-ban-ha-guc-duc-mot-cdv-mexico-bat-ngo-lay-duoc-vo-421-188930.html\">Lozano ghi b\u00e0n h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110\u1ee9c, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Mexico b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ee3</span><br />\r\nQu\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Mexico c\u1ea7u h\u00f4n b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i ngay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i k\u1ebft c\u00f3 h\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dkvd-thua-soc-ngay-ra-quan-low-da-thuc-su-het-bai-421-188808.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/dkvd-thua-soc-ngay-ra-quan-low-da-thuc-su-het-bai.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dkvd-thua-soc-ngay-ra-quan-low-da-thuc-su-het-bai-421-188808.html\">\u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c thua s\u1ed1c ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n: Low \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ebft b\u00e0i?</span><br />\r\nKh\u00f4ng ai mong ch\u1edd \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-world-cup-2018-h1-461-188750.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/lozano.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-world-cup-2018-h1-461-188750.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br />\r\nNh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 khoa h\u1ecdc. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"380","checkdouble":"189012"},{"date":"10:47 20/06","title":"Pepe: \"Ronaldo t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec m\u00e0 \u1ea7m \u0129\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/pepe-ronaldo-toa-sang-co-gi-ma-am-i.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh ai c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho m\u00ecnh \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ra c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt \u201cnh\u00ecn v\u1eady v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1eady\u201d.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian:</em> 22h ng\u00e0y 20/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>Rostov Arena (th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Rostov-on-Don)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Uruguay -0.97*0:2*0.91 Saudi Arabia<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u -0.93*3*0.85 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia-va-du-doan-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia 22h ng\u00e0y 20/6</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Uruguay kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Saudi Arabia</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia. \u1ede b\u1ea3ng A, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ai C\u1eadp 1-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 ra nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Uruguay. Trong \u0111\u00f3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. 14 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c La Celeste \u0111\u01b0a ra song m\u00e3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 89, nh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Jose Gimenez xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gimenez danh dau vao luoi Ai Cap\" title=\"Gimenez danh dau vao luoi Ai Cap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Gimenez-danh-dau-vao-luoi-Ai-Cap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Uruguay v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ai C\u1eadp 1-0 nh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Gimenez ph\u00fat 89</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc n\u01a1i Uruguay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Oscar Tabarez th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n qua l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t b\u1ed5ng b\u1ecb c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 cao to c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, Uruguay c\u0169ng phung ph\u00ed. Ri\u00eang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Luis Suarez \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ai C\u1eadp. Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1ec7t nh\u1ecdc c\u00f9ng Barcelona, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ed1 9 c\u1ee7a Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb v\u1eaft ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c. Anh t\u1ecf ra n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 trong di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi-421-188597.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi-421-188597.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Ai C\u1eadp 0-1 Uruguay: Salah bu\u1ed3n, Suarez n\u00e0o c\u00f3 vui g\u00ec</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc c\u1ee7a hai ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Trong khi Salah bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 thua v\u00e0o ph\u00fat...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1. Uruguay kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00edch \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 d\u1ed3n d\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd th\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia, gi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh ni\u1ec1m vui tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho Uruguay. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen n\u00e0y. G\u1ea7n 2 n\u0103m qua, Uruguay ch\u01a1i 17 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu l\u1eabn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng c\u00f3 7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Golovin gop dau giay vao 3/5 ban thang cua Nga truoc Saudi Arabia\" title=\"Golovin g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 3/5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Nga tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/may-bay-cho-tuyen-saudi-arabia-phut-lua-tren-troi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Saudi Arabia b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 sau tr\u1eadn thua Nga</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd: Uruguay th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 7 tr\u1eadn trong \u0111\u00f3. C\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn h\u1ecd th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh ph\u00e1 &ldquo;b\u00ea t\u00f4ng&rdquo; v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do Tabarez d\u1eabn d\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSaudi Arabia \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3. Tr\u00ean BXH b\u1ea3ng A l\u00fac n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi 0 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 thua thi\u1ec7t. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi Nga \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ai C\u1eadp r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay (20/6), Saudi Arabia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 thua Uruguay. Trong th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng, &ldquo;Chim \u01b0ng xanh&rdquo; s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Uruguay kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH bang A\" title=\"BXH bang A\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/BXH-bang-A.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Saudi Arabia \u0111\u1ee9ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng A</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</em><br>\r\n- Uruguay ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 7/17 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua<br>\r\n- Uruguay ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 4/10 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\n- Trong 7 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean, Uruguay ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 tr\u1eadn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2 b\u00e0n, 1 tr\u1eadn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn: Saudi Arabia (+2)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean quan \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia s\u1ebd thi\u1ebfu t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng l\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf. \u1ede m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Uruguay c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i th\u00ec l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 1-0 v\u00e0 2-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Uruguay \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Gi\u1ea3 s\u1eed c\u00f3 s\u1edbm v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, xem ra La Celeste c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 10 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Uruguay ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 l\u00e0 t\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Oscar Tabarez noi ve tran Ai Cap vs Uruguay\" title=\"Oscar Tabarez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/hlv-uruguay-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-truoc-ai-cap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV&nbsp;Tabarez \u0111\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0 ri\u00eang cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n 4 b\u00e0n m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. H\u01a1n 2 n\u0103m qua, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Uruguay \u0111\u1ea1t ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n n\u00e0y. C\u00f2n Saudi Arabia, lo\u1ea1i m\u00e0n b\u1ecb Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t 0-5 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean, c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3/15 l\u1ea7n kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi gian.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Saudi Arabia l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n. Uruguay l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</em><br>\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 4/10 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 1/11 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 4/15 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\n- Saudi Arabia kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong 3 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1eeba qua<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn: \u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (U 3)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- <strong>Saudi Arabia kh\u00f4ng thua c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t</strong> (t\u1eeb 2 tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng)<br>\r\n- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1:</strong> Uruguay th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 10 (O 9 1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 (O 4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Uruguay nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 (-4 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a Uruguay nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 (-2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong hi\u1ec7p 1 (-1)<br>\r\n- S\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn (-3)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"379","checkdouble":"189013"},{"date":"11:02 20/06","title":"\u0110T Anh nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/dt-anh-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-tu-tru-cot.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dele Alli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tusinia, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Gareth Southgate x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dele Alli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh v\u1edbi Tunisia ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Anh ch\u01a1i ph\u00eda sau b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane v\u00e0 Raheem Sterling. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Spurs kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dele Alli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Dele Alli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/dt-anh-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-tu-tru-cot.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Dele Alli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 80, Alli ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Ruben Loftus-Cheek, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 Anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1, h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 Alli l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Gareth Southgate kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng r\u00fat Alli ra ngh\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, Tam s\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Harry Kane \u1edf nh\u1eefng\u00a0ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Southgate n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Alli</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dele Alli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tusinia, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Gareth Southgate x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Southgate phat bieu ve tran Anh vs Tunisia\" title=\"Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gareth Southgate hy v\u1ecdng Alli kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAlli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb \u0111au \u1edf \u0111\u00f9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i theo d\u00f5i t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Alli\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee3i k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Alli s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Alli c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i: \u201cT\u00f4i \u1ed5n. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Panama, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 thua B\u1ec9 0-3 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Panama c\u00f2n B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tunisia, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng G.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"378","checkdouble":"189015"},{"date":"11:54 20/06","title":"\u0110T B\u1ec9 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/dt-bi-chuan-bi-doi-mat-voi-nguy-co-lon-chua-tung-co.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ngay sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV B\u1ec9 chia s\u1ebb n\u1ed7i lo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 lo ngay ng\u00e1y c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/bi-vs-panama-bang-g-463-188832.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Panama 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1</span>, v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Dries Mertens c\u00f9ng c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Romelu Lukaku. D\u00f9 ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean ngay sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, B\u1ec9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i CLB. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia kh\u1eafp ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ngay t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m di\u1ec5n ra VCK World Cup, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hazard-chelsea-phai-chi-dam-moi-giu-duoc-toi-421-188884.html\" target=\"_blank\">Eden Hazard kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1eadm n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n anh</span>. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung, t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u00f9ng tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV B\u1ec9 chia s\u1ebb n\u1ed7i lo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y\" title=\"B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV B\u1ec9 chia s\u1ebb n\u1ed7i lo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0 c\u1ef1u tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia &ndash; \u00f4ng Vital Borkelmans cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac r\u1ed3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Courtois c\u0169ng v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1edbn, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111i. Courtois r\u1ea5t th\u00edch cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Chelse v\u00e0 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c, m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi Fellaini v\u00e0 Alderweireld. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ra \u0111i. V\u1edbi Fellaini, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n, trong khi Alderweireld l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a \u0110T&rdquo; &ndash; c\u1ef1u tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV B\u1ec9 chia s\u1ebb n\u1ed7i lo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-30-panama-khi-moi-loi-khen-di-kem-voi-mot-chu-nhung-421-188888.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/0.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-30-panama-khi-moi-loi-khen-di-kem-voi-mot-chu-nhung-421-188888.html\">B\u1ec9&hellip; v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Panama: Khi m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi khen \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ch\u1eef &ldquo;nh\u01b0ng&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 3-0 Panama l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec l\u01b0\u1ee3t ra qu\u00e2n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i c\u00e1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u1ea5t an \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ec1 d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf v\u1eabn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lukaku-lap-ky-luc-ghi-ban-khung-fan-mu-lai-loi-morata-ra-de-biu-421-188880.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/lukaku-lap-ky-luc-ghi-ban-khung-fan-mu-lai-loi-morata-ra-de-biu.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lukaku-lap-ky-luc-ghi-ban-khung-fan-mu-lai-loi-morata-ra-de-biu-421-188880.html\">Lukaku l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n kh\u1ee7ng, fan M.U l\u1ea1i l\u00f4i&hellip; Morata ra d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Panama m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Romelu Lukaku l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c kh\u1ee7ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188867.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188867.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 c\u00f3 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khai th\u00f4ng ngay sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 v\u1edbi si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Mertens v\u00e0 c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf gi\u00e0nh th\u1ebf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"377","checkdouble":"189016"}]}